1925;;The Tower of Lies;;American;;Victor Sjostrom;;Norma Shearer, Lon Chaney;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Tower_of_Lies;;Jan (Lon Chaney) is a Swedish farmer and Glory (Norma Shearer) is his beloved daughter, who saves him from bankruptcy by eloping to the big city with their rapacious landlord, driving Jan to madness.